steps.html_instructions: Head west on Kühlinger Straße toward Hinter dem Richthause

Slight left onto Quedlinburger Straße/B79
Continue to follow B79
Merge onto B6 via the ramp to A14/Bernburg/Aschersleben
Take exit 20-Schkeuditzer Kreuz to merge onto A9 toward München/Erfurt
Take exit 76-München-Schwabing on the left toward Mittlerer Ring Ost/Messe / ICM

Merge onto Schenkendorfstraße/B2R
Continue to follow B2R
